      <title>台湾承认中国内地公民同性婚姻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/taiwan-recognizes-same-sex-marriages-involving-chinese-nationals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾表示将承认与中国大陆人士有关的同性婚姻，此举将使这个民主岛国的数百对夫妇受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/taiwan-recognizes-same-sex-marriages-involving-chinese-nationals</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 03:08:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥普拉邀请好莱坞一线明星参加市政厅活动，为哈里斯助阵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/oprah-enlists-hollywood-a-listers-for-town-hall-to-boost-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯周四在密歇根州精心制作的虚拟市政厅会议上邀请脱口秀传奇人物奥普拉·温弗瑞和一群好莱坞一线明星参加，以期聚集势头和资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/oprah-enlists-hollywood-a-listers-for-town-hall-to-boost-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 02:39:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢克森称新西兰可以与特朗普或哈里斯领导下的美国合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/new-zealand-can-work-with-us-under-trump-or-harris-luxon-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰总理克里斯托弗·卢克森表示，无论谁赢得 11 月的总统大选，新西兰都将探索与美国日益增长的经济机会，同时强调新西兰已从全球自由贸易中获得了巨大利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/new-zealand-can-work-with-us-under-trump-or-harris-luxon-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 02:13:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚国王访华寻求高铁资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/malaysia-s-king-to-seek-funds-for-high-speed-rail-on-china-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，马来西亚国王计划向中国投资者寻求资金，用于马来西亚与新加坡之间价值数十亿美元的高铁项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/malaysia-s-king-to-seek-funds-for-high-speed-rail-on-china-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 01:30:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>媒体称日本考虑与中国达成协议解除海鲜进口禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/japan-eyes-deal-to-end-chinese-ban-on-seafood-imports-media-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据日本媒体报道，中国和日本可能即将就北京去年为应对福岛核电站向海洋排放处理过的放射性废水而实施的进口日本海产品禁令取得突破。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/japan-eyes-deal-to-end-chinese-ban-on-seafood-imports-media-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 01:28:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称犹太选民“与选举失败有很大关系”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/trump-vows-to-bring-back-travel-ban-bar-refugees-from-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普在反犹太主义峰会上表示，如果他最终输掉总统大选，犹太选民应该为此负责，并抱怨自己在支持以色列后“没有得到公正的对待”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/trump-vows-to-bring-back-travel-ban-bar-refugees-from-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 00:44:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾最高法院将就死刑法律挑战作出裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/top-taiwan-court-to-rule-on-legal-challenge-to-death-penalty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾宪法法院即将就台湾是否应废除死刑作出裁决，这是对其作为亚洲最进步社会之一的声誉的关键考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/top-taiwan-court-to-rule-on-legal-challenge-to-death-penalty</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万斯和沃尔兹在副总裁辩论前举行 CEO 会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/vance-walz-hold-dueling-ceo-meetings-with-vp-debate-looming</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统候选人在华盛顿的竞选会议上互相拉拢首席执行官，双方竞选团队都试图在这场极其激烈的竞争中赢得主要商界领袖的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/vance-walz-hold-dueling-ceo-meetings-with-vp-debate-looming</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 18:35:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰总理着眼于经济反弹，度过艰难的第一年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/new-zealand-s-luxon-eyes-economic-rebound-after-tough-first-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰总理克里斯托弗·卢克森 (Christopher Luxon) 上任第一年充满动荡，可能出现经济衰退、预算赤字扩大和种族关系紧张，他可以期待 2025 年利率下降将推动经济复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/new-zealand-s-luxon-eyes-economic-rebound-after-tough-first-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度禁止 Axis Bank 子公司管理新债发行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/india-bars-axis-bank-unit-from-managing-new-debt-offerings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度资本市场监管机构禁止 Axis Capital Ltd. 担任印度公司新债发行的管理人，这是该国证券市场的最新一次打击行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/india-bars-axis-bank-unit-from-managing-new-debt-offerings</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:05:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
